00:01:28,002 --> 00:01:33,004
We begin with a Thinking Observation.

11
00:01:33,004 --> 00:01:39,009
Today we observe a strange pheonenon using coins.

12
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:46,002
Hold up a single one yen and two ten yen coins between your fingers.

13
00:01:48,007 --> 00:01:51,008
This ten yen coin remains above.

14
00:01:51,009 --> 00:01:56,002
The lower two coins drop.

15
00:01:56,003 --> 00:02:00,005
The one yen coin above and the 10 yen coin below.

16
00:02:00,006 --> 00:02:03,005
If we drop these two coins...

17
00:02:07,005 --> 00:02:10,001
The one yen coin ends up on top.

18
00:02:12,002 --> 00:02:15,008
Did they switch en route?

19
00:02:15,008 --> 00:02:18,000
Let's do it once more.

20
00:02:22,005 --> 00:02:26,003
Once more the one yen coin went to the bottom.

21
00:02:26,003 --> 00:02:30,002
As we thought they switched positions.

22
00:02:30,002 --> 00:02:35,003
Let's try a different combination.

23
00:02:35,003 --> 00:02:38,009
We add another 10 yen coin underneath.

24
00:02:38,009 --> 00:02:46,005
Leaving the single ten yen coin above in place, we drop the three below.

25
00:02:46,006 --> 00:02:50,001
Doing so, we confirm the three coins have changed position.

26
00:02:50,002 --> 00:02:55,001
Will the one yen coin end up at the bottom?

27
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,002
The one yen coin ended up in the middle.

28
00:03:06,004 --> 00:03:08,006
Let's try once more.

29
00:03:13,006 --> 00:03:15,006
It's the same.

30
00:03:17,009 --> 00:03:20,007
Let's try to organize this on paper.

31
00:03:22,007 --> 00:03:31,002
At the start 1 yen 10 yen became 10 yen 1 yen.

32
00:03:31,003 --> 00:03:38,000
Next if we add another 10 yen coin below.

33
00:03:38,001 --> 00:03:40,004
It changed this way.

34
00:03:40,004 --> 00:03:42,007
We don't understand this well.

35
00:03:42,007 --> 00:03:48,003
What will happen with a different arrangement.

36
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:56,003
This time we dropped the one yen coin in the middle.

37
00:04:01,002 --> 00:04:04,008
And it ended up underneath.

38
00:04:06,006 --> 00:04:09,003
Let's also confirm this on paper.

39
00:04:13,004 --> 00:04:15,008
Looking carefully at the results..

40
00:04:15,009 --> 00:04:18,006
We can see some regularity.

41
