83
00:09:24,007 --> 00:09:27,006
and stop right away."

84
00:09:27,006 --> 00:09:34,003
But magnest ought not stick to aluminum.

85
00:09:34,004 --> 00:09:38,001
Why should this happen?

86
00:09:38,002 --> 00:09:43,001
This is connected to a propery between magnets and aluminum.

87
00:09:43,002 --> 00:09:48,002
Magnets don't stick to aluminum, but it conducts electricity.

88
